  <!-- ══ QUEST BOOK TAB ══ -->
  <div class="section" id="questbook">
    <div class="qb-wrap">

      <!-- Black Menagerie Archetypes -->
      <div>
        <p class="qb-section-label">The Black Menagerie</p>
        <h2 class="qb-section-title">Five archetypes.<br><em>All of them, yours.</em></h2>
        <p class="qb-section-body">You don't get assigned one. You rotate through all five — so by Week 12 you know viscerally which one is home and which ones stretch you.</p>
        <div class="qb-archetypes-grid">
          <div class="qb-archetype-card">
            <span class="qb-archetype-emoji">🐘</span>
            <div class="qb-archetype-name">Black Elephant</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-desc">Builds new infrastructure. Comfortable with no map. Grows things in unexpected conditions.</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-quest">What do we all know but haven't spoken aloud?</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-archetype-card">
            <span class="qb-archetype-emoji">🦢</span>
            <div class="qb-archetype-name">Black Swan</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-desc">Holds the emotional climate. Creates belonging. Makes safe spaces to think.</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-quest">What change is coming that we haven't named yet?</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-archetype-card">
            <span class="qb-archetype-emoji">🪼</span>
            <div class="qb-archetype-name">Black Jellyfish</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-desc">Holds the long view. Names signals everyone else calls noise. Comfortable in uncertainty.</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-quest">What are we feeling in our bodies about what's next?</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-archetype-card">
            <span class="qb-archetype-emoji">🐑</span>
            <div class="qb-archetype-name">Black Sheep</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-desc">Synthesizes and makes meaning. Keeper of the story. Collects what matters.</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-quest">What playful disruption wants to emerge?</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-archetype-card">
            <span class="qb-archetype-emoji">🐢</span>
            <div class="qb-archetype-name">Black Marsh Turtle</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-desc">Transforms raw material — experience, conflict, data — into something usable and beautiful.</div>
            <div class="qb-archetype-quest">What do we need to slow down with? Where is rest calling?</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="qb-divider"></div>

      <!-- 12-Week Arc -->
      <div>
        <p class="qb-section-label">The Full Map</p>
        <h2 class="qb-section-title">12 weeks.<br><em>12 worlds.</em></h2>
        <p class="qb-section-body">This is the backdrop of the Quest over the 12 weeks. Each week the genre changes. You keep everything that is portable about yourself. A question waiting at every stage. The arc follows the traditional (Western) Hero's Journey.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--gold);margin-top:0.75rem;opacity:0.8;">★ = Milestone session</p>
        <div class="qb-arc-grid">
          <div class="qb-arc-week">
            <div class="qb-arc-week-num">Week 01 · Witness ★</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-stage">Status Quo</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-theme">Safety · Black Elephant</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-world">🌿 Ancestral Village at the edge of a great forest</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-blank">"My character's name in 2032 is ___"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-arc-week">
            <div class="qb-arc-week-num">Week 02</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-stage">Call to Adventure</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-theme">Identity · Black Jellyfish</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-world">🗺️ Edge of the Known Map</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-blank">"I am a ___ who ___ [verb of transformation]"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-arc-week">
            <div class="qb-arc-week-num">Week 03</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-stage">Assistance</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-theme">Power · Black Swan</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-world">🍄 Underground Mycelial Network</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-blank">"I work with/for ___ [community]"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-arc-week qb-milestone">
            <div class="qb-milestone-badge">★ Milestone</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-week-num">Week 04 · Witness ★</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-stage">Departure</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-theme">Integrity · Black Sheep</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-world">🌊 Ocean Floor Civilization</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-blank">"The world I inhabit has learned to ___ [paradigm shift]"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-arc-week">
            <div class="qb-arc-week-num">Week 05</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-stage">Trials</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-theme">Possibility · Black Marsh Turtle</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-world">⚡ Solarpunk City mid-transition</div>
            <div class="qb-arc-blank">"I am known for my ___ [signature gift]"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qb-arc-week">
            <div class="qb-arc-week-num">Week 06</div>
